UID:68f17e4861706d28001e1906@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Digital Navigator One-On-One Tech Help each Wednesday from 10:
 00 a.m. -12:00 p.m. in the library. Need help with digital questions or jo
 b searches? This free program is in partnership with American Connection C
 orps & The Washington County Cooperative Library Services. Call the librar
 y at 503 324-1382 to schedule a session.\nIf no appointments are scheduled
  drop in tech help will be available.\nThe Digital Navigator Program (DNP)
  is a free service made possible by a partnership\nbetween Washington Coun
 ty Cooperative Library Services (WCCLS) and the Washington\nCounty Broadba
 nd Action Team. The DNP is funded in part by American Connections\nCorps\,
  an AmeriCorps program dedicated to advancing economic prosperity by bridg
 ing\nthe digital divide. This project is being supported\, in part\, by fe
 deral award number\nSLFRP0228 awarded to Washington County by the U.S. Dep
 artment of the Treasury.
LOCATION:Banks Public Library
