BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Prepárate con Pedro | Prepare with Pedro: Earthquakes
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260325T173000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260325T190000Z
UID:698e47f74dacf581ff7ae5f9@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Acompaña a Pedro el Pingüino de la Cruz Roja Americana en un
 a divertida introducción a la preparación para terremotos. A través de 
 cuentos y actividades\, los niños aprenderán qué hacer durante un terre
 moto y cómo prepararse en familia.\nRecomendado para niños de 4 a 8 año
 s y sus cuidadores. Registrarse requerido.\nJoin Pedro the Penguin from th
 e American Red Cross for a fun\, kid-friendly introduction to earthquake p
 reparedness. Through stories\, videos\, and simple activities\, children w
 ill learn what earthquakes are\, what to do if one happens\, and how famil
 ies can prepare together. This interactive program helps kids feel confide
 nt—not scared—while building important safety skills in an age-appropr
 iate way.\nRecommended for children ages 4–8 and their caregivers. Regis
 tration required.
LOCATION:Hillsboro Public Library\, Shute Park
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/698e47f74dacf581ff7ae5f9
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
