UID:6983d727cbf1533ca5361860@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Improve your English fluency! This program is designed for ind
 ividuals who are ready to enhance their speaking skills in a friendly and 
 encouraging atmosphere. Whether you're a beginner or intermediate learner\
 , join us to build confidence\, expand vocabulary\, and connect with other
 s on a language-learning journey. No registration required - just bring yo
 ur enthusiasm and let's chat in English!
