DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260506T200000Z
UID:6994ef904a9fd98b7f7eac1e@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Learn to use Google Docs with a Google account. Explore format
 ting\, menus\, inserting objects\, and sharing\, uploading\, and downloadi
 ng documents in this cloud-based class. Learn modern job search skills\, i
 ncluding navigating online postings\, spotting red flags\, extracting key 
 qualifications\, and creating a strong Indeed profile. Perfect for beginne
 rs or those refining their approach to stand out to employers.
LOCATION:Hillsboro Public Library\, Shute Park
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6994ef904a9fd98b7f7eac1e
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
