DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260410T210000Z
UID:697a404ed2bbe265eb2a7b3d@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Need help installing an app on your new phone\, configuring a 
 webcam for Zoom\, borrowing and downloading an e-book\, or filling out an 
 online job application? You can make an appointment to speak to our friend
 ly and knowledgeable Digital Navigator\nevery Friday between 10:00 and 12:
 30\n(follow the link below to sign up for a spot)\, or you can\ndrop in be
 tween 12:45 and 2:00\nto get assistance for these and other tech-related i
 ssues. Bring your own device or use one of our computers.\nClick\nhere\nto
  make a 30-minute appointment with our Digital Navigator.\nThe Digital Nav
 igator program has been made possible by a partnership with AmeriCorps and
  the Washington County Broadband Action Team.
LOCATION:Forest Grove City Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/697a404ed2bbe265eb2a7b3d
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
