BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:All Ages Storytime Session 2
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T171500Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T181500Z
UID:69420a73caa2e62f002097c7@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Welcome preschoolers birth to six and their caregivers!\nAtten
 ding All Ages Storytime is a great way to build a caring bond between chil
 d and adult.\nIn this program\, you and your child will sing songs\, liste
 n to stories\, dance to music\, engage in interactive play\, and so much m
 ore!\n15 minutes of playtime follows each session.\nThis is the winter ses
 sion of this program and it runs January 7 - March 18. All Ages Storytime 
 Session 1 takes a break March 25. Spring Session will begin April 1\, 2026
 \nSpecial Note:  February 4 & 11\, 2026 will be a playtime session only fr
 om 9:30 a.m. - 11:15 a.m.\nArrive anytime between 9:30 a.m. - 10:00a.m. to
  enjoy this program. We understand how difficult it is to be punctual with
  children. Playtime is just as beneficial as the storytime.\nThe library o
 pens at 10:00 a.m.
LOCATION:Sherwood Public Library\, Community Room\, first floor.
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69420a73caa2e62f002097c7
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
