BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Shameless Romance Book Club
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260408T013000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260408T023000Z
UID:69a22242b0595799c09fde6c@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Our Shameless Romance Book Club’s next read is\nShe Doesn't 
 Have a Clue\nby Jenny Elder!\nA high-end wedding on a private island sound
 s like something out of a dream\, but when the groom is your editor and ex
 -fiancé\, it’s more like a nightmare. Bestselling mystery author Kate V
 alentine planned to get through the ordeal with fake smiles\, that is unti
 l the bride is poisoned\, and Kate is the one to discover the body. Now Ka
 te finds herself in a real-life mystery that is shockingly similar to the 
 plot of her latest novel. And the only person who seems willing to help Ka
 te catch the killer is her biggest romantic regret\, Jake Hawkins. Kate is
  a pro at solving fictional mysteries\, but are her skills only make belie
 ve? Or can she and Jake catch the culprit before it’s too late?\nReserve
  a copy here\n. Also available in eBook\, downloadable audiobook\, and pr
 eloaded audiobook (Playaway) formats.\nWant to read ahead?\nCheck out the
  Shameless Romance Book Club’s schedule and titles for the rest of 2026!
LOCATION:Aloha Community Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69a22242b0595799c09fde6c
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
