SUMMARY:Drop-in Art at West Slope: Salty Watercolor Clouds
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T220000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260402T000000Z
UID:69b1aa35db89981d9df94fc1@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Every first Wednesday of the month from 3-5pm\, drop-in to Wes
 t Slope Community Library to pick out some new books and make art together
 . This month\, learn about the cool ways that salt changes your painting a
 s we make some rain clouds with watercolor! Program is come and go. We p
 rovide the materials and the clean up! No registration required.
LOCATION:West Slope Community Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69b1aa35db89981d9df94fc1
