DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260312T190000Z
UID:6983d87acbf1533ca536187e@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Talk about death. Learn about life. Death and dying aren't oft
 en talked about\, but they touch us all. Join us to explore these themes i
 n a relaxed\, safe atmosphere. Death Cafe is a discussion group rather tha
 n a grief support or counseling session. Hosted by Wade McJacobs. Registra
 tion recommended.
LOCATION:Beaverton City Library\, Meeting Rooms A & B
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6983d87acbf1533ca536187e
