UID:69926b2bb48451fc3c02fccd@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Calling all children in upper elementary grades and above who 
 love graphic novels! Grow your literacy skills in a supportive learning en
 vironment where respect and appreciation for differences is encouraged.\nL
 ed by former faculty in special education and supported by teacher candida
 tes and preservice speech-language pathology students\, participants will 
 engage in book study activities\, vocabulary building exercises and langua
 ge and literacy skills appropriate for a wide range of learners.\nRegistra
 tion required.
