DESCRIPTION:Digital Navigator Tech Help is held every Saturday in the libr
 ary except the 3rd Saturday of the month (when the library hosts computer 
 classes) from 10:00 a.m to 2:00 p.m. through July 25. Need help with devi
 ces? Have technology-related questions? Want help with job searches? Br
 ing your own device or use library computers.\nThese are drop-in hours onl
 y\, so first come\, first served.\nThis free program is provided by a visi
 ting Digital Navigator and is in partnership with AmeriCorps & Washington 
 County Cooperative Library Services.\nAlso see our\nTech Help Appointments
  offered by library staff.
