BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:This is Vietnamese Portland Project Talk
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260506T013000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260506T024500Z
UID:699f3c3b403a4e5652dd7202@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:We welcome you to join us for a presentation on the Vietnamese
  Portland: Memory\, History\, Community project. This event will include a
  presentation on the history of the project\, current activities\, and how
  to get involved with the archive. This archive is being built in order to
  ensure that a more inclusive history of Portland is preserved\, including
  the rich\, diverse\, and important contributions of Vietnamese Americans 
 to the city and its growth since 1975. Our growing archive is largely hous
 ed at vietnameseportland.org.
LOCATION:Hillsboro Public Library\, Brookwood
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/699f3c3b403a4e5652dd7202
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
