DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260403T190000Z
UID:6983d6c0707481383708e29a@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Connect with friends\, neighbors\, and fellow community member
 s in a welcoming space for meaningful discussion. Each month\, we’ll exp
 lore a new topic designed to spark engaging conversations. Come share your
  perspective and hear new ideas as you get to know others in your communit
 y. This event is co-sponsored by Viva Village. Registration recommended.
LOCATION:Beaverton City Library\, Meeting Rooms A & B
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6983d6c0707481383708e29a
