END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Digital Navigator: One-On-One Tech Help
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260424T170000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260424T210000Z
UID:6983d66bcbf6405d35665ee6@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:In a one-on-one session\, Digital Navigators can answer questi
 ons about devices\, navigating websites\, getting started with tech\, and 
 more. Digital Navigation is available in English\, Spanish\, and Arabic.\n
