 Wednesday: 12–6 PM\; Thursday: 11 AM - 5 PM. Try out our 3D printers\, C
 ricuts\, sewing machines\, and more!\nWelcome to our makerspace\, DAM (Des
 ign And Make)! During Open Lab hours\, the makerspace is open for all ages
