UID:6983d66bcbf6405d35665ee2@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:In a one-on-one session\, Digital Navigators can answer questi
 ons about devices\, navigating websites\, getting started with tech\, and 
 more. Digital Navigation is available in English\, Spanish\, and Arabic.\n
 Appointments are on Fridays from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. Schedule online (\nhtt
 ps://beavertonlibrary.libcal.com/appointments?lid=3627&g=25012\n) or by c
 alling the library at 503-644-2197.
