DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260324T220000Z
UID:6983e240a5d80ac492705a5f@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Create different types of paper airplanes and watch them fly!
  Grades K-5 with family.
LOCATION:Beaverton City Library\, Meeting Rooms A & B
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6983e240a5d80ac492705a5f
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Bloodwork NW Blood Drive
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260508T170000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260508T230000Z
UID:697a603c4a9fd98b7f7a6299@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Make saving lives a habit in 2026 and be the change!\nBecoming
  a regular blood donor with the local\, independent\, non-profit organizat
 ion Bloodworks NW helps our friends\, family\, and neighbors being treated
  in 95% of hospitals across Oregon & Washington.\nThe library is hosting a
 nother Bloodworks NW mobile drive on Friday\, May 8\, from 10:00 am to 4:0
 0 pm. Sign up for your 1-hour appointment online at\nhttps://donate.bloodw
 orksnw.or...\nMust be 16+ to donate. Be sure to eat a hearty meal and drin
 k plenty of fluids prior to donating.
LOCATION:Forest Grove City Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/697a603c4a9fd98b7f7a6299
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
