DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260403T190000Z
UID:698bb08881b67dfe32a59eff@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Kids with varying learning styles and abilities come together 
 in a safe and supportive environment. Children who may need visual and/or 
 communication supports\, a more predictable routine\, or adapted materials
  due to a motor impairment are welcome. Ages 3-5. Pre-register at mpebly@
 pdx.edu.
