BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:OMSI Presents: React-O-Blast
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260326T210000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260326T220000Z
UID:6983e27fcbf1533ca5361941@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:OMSI staff bring science to life with demos that let kids see\
 , hear\, and feel the wild world of matter in action - from reactions you 
 can predict to surprises that pop and fizz. Audience participants experien
 ce what makes chemical reactions tick\, how physical and chemical changes 
 differ\, and why safety is always part of the experiment. Designed especia
 lly for curious minds in grades K–8\, this program turns science into an
  adventure. Grades K-8.
LOCATION:Beaverton City Library\, Meeting Rooms A & B
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6983e27fcbf1533ca5361941
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
