BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Citizenship [at Bethany Library Annex]
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260414T003000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260414T023000Z
UID:69866b60834cbb3dea2c14cb@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Free citizenship classes provided by SOAR Immigration Legal Se
 rvices. Classes are designed to prepare you for the US naturalization inte
 rview and exam. Study US history and civics lessons (100 questions on citi
 zenship exam)\; improve your English speaking\, listening\, writing\, and 
 reading\; practice for the naturalization interview\; and review the N-400
  application. Classes are taught in English\, with resources in Spanish an
 d other languages.
LOCATION:Bethany Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69866b60834cbb3dea2c14cb
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
