BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:"Here We Are Again Still\," a Play by Christian O'Reilly
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T210000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T223000Z
UID:699df15781b67dfe32a88e6b@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an 80-minute theatrical production of "Here We Are
  Again Still" by Irish playwright Christian O'Reilly. An Irish widower spe
 nds all his nights sitting by himself on a bench outside his housing compl
 ex. As his stubborn neighbor repeatedly urges him to get up and experience
  life\, and a down-on-his-luck young newcomer decides to start frequenting
  the very same bench\, the three lost souls find themselves forging an une
 xpected connection. "Here We Are Again Still" is a funny\, heartfelt ode t
 o community\, finding purpose\, and the beauty of the unknown. 80 minutes\
 , no intermission. Best for ages 17+. Featuring Ted Rooney\, Carla Grant\,
  and Ben Lawrence. Doors at 1:30 PM.
LOCATION:Beaverton City Library\, Auditorium
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/699df15781b67dfe32a88e6b
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
