BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Music for All Ages: WindSync
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260422T230000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260423T000000Z
UID:69a4c0c4403a4e5652dde09e@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Vibrant quintet\nWindSync\nbrings their personal performance s
 tyle\, combined with the ensemble’s three-pronged mission of artistry\, 
 education\, and community-building\, back to our library in a program for 
 the whole family. With a repertoire spanning from folk\, classical\, and c
 ontemporary works\, find out why WindSync is known as "a group of virtuoso
 s who are also wonderful people\, too." Held in the Community Room. Presen
 ted in partnership with\nChamber Music Northwest\n.
LOCATION:Tualatin Public Library\, Community Room
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69a4c0c4403a4e5652dde09e
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
