DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T230000Z
UID:692f2bf5d923da4200b34ebe@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Practice your moves in a casual setting with other players of 
 these ancient board games. Students of all ages & adults are welcome! All 
 levels are welcome!\nPractica tus movimientos de ajedrez en un ambiente in
 formal con otros jugadores. ¡Estudiantes de todas las edades y adultos so
 n bienvenidos! ¡Todos los niveles son bienvenidos!
LOCATION:Hillsboro Public Library\, Shute Park
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/692f2bf5d923da4200b34ebe
