UID:69726e522c65973d001959e5@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Understanding Grief Saturday March 14\nth\nfrom 10:30 a.m. -12
 :00 p.m. at the library.\nJoin Becky Oswald\, Thanatologist and Grief Educ
 ator\,  to expand your understanding of grief and acquire tools for coping
  with grief in your life. This workshop helps participants recognize the m
 any kinds of grief connected to different types of loss and understand tha
 t grief is a normal response. Attendees will explore how processing grief 
