UID:68a6165828109b6cd7302ab2@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:3\nrd\nSundays + final session: March 15\, April 19\, May 17\
 , & May 31 | 4 – 5 pm | Brookwood\nLearning public speaking skills earl
 y builds confidence\, promotes understanding and critical thinking\, and c
 an be a foundation for lifelong success – plus it’s fun! This interact
 ive program teaches public speaking and respectful debating. Led by City o
 f Hillsboro Communications Manager Patrick Preston.\nFor youth grades 5\nt
 h\n– 8\nth\n.\nThis is a series of four classes. By registering\, you ar
 e signing up for the full Spring season.
