BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Children's Day | Día del Niños
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260430T230000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260501T010000Z
UID:69ab7839db89981d9df8dc1f@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:It's Children's Day\, so of course that means we're having a b
 ig\, fun\, family party! This year we'll be learning circus tricks from Sp
 oon Circus\, painting our faces\, eating cake\, and of course\, giving out
  free books!\nThis program is for all ages\, and is in partnership with Al
 l Together Now.\nEs el Día del Niño\, así que\, por supuesto\, ¡vamos 
 a tener una gran y divertida fiesta familiar! Este año aprenderemos truco
 s de circo con Spoon Circus\, nos pintaremos la cara\, comeremos pastel y\
 , por supuesto\,\n¡regalaremos libros!\nEste programa es para todas las e
 dades y se realiza en colaboración con All Together Now.
LOCATION:Cornelius Public Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69ab7839db89981d9df8dc1f
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
