DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260402T001500Z
UID:698d0a391e64afd01e5ace65@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Read to a certified therapy dog in a stress-free environment!\
 nSign-up for a 20-minute reading session.\nThis program will help improve 
 your child's reading skills and they get to make a new friend by reading a
 loud to a therapy dog.\nThe dogs and handlers are from\nDove Lewis Portlan
 d Area Canine Therapy Teams\nand\nPet Partners®
LOCATION:Garden Home Community Library\, Enter the building through the Re
 c Center's main entrance and walk through the building to the library and 
 check in at the front desk
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/698d0a391e64afd01e5ace65
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
