BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Art Studio Jr: Paint-a-Pot
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T230000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T000000Z
UID:696ec503491b809c6f13cb2d@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Are you ready to create your latest masterpiece? Join us in th
 is process-based program as we explore different artists\, mediums and mov
 ements!\nThis month we will be painting mini succulent pots!\nParticipants
  must be in grades K-5.\nRegistration is required\n. Held in the Makerspac
 e.
