DESCRIPTION:Topic To Be Determined\nThe Ge\nnealogical Society is dedicate
 d to promoting the study of genealogy and the preservation of family herit
 age. Monthly meetings host speakers for instruction in family research. To
 pics range widely from local to international record search and use.\nChe
 ck out the website for more details:\nGenealogical Society of Wash. Co. we
