 on supports\, a more predictable routine\, or adapted materials due to a m
 otor impairment are welcome. Pre-register at\nmpebly@pdx.edu\n\; we can se
 nd materials home ahead of time.\nBilingual sessions are held at Shute Par
 k Library on 1st and 3rd Fridays.
