  smartphone\, or updating your email contacts? Volunteers will be availabl
 e at Open Lab to answer questions. Bring your own computer\, tablet\, cell
 phone\, or e-reader with you to get assistance or use one of our laptops t
 o practice. Be sure to have any usernames and passwords available for acc
 ounts you need help navigating.\nOur spring session of Technology Open Lab
  meets 1-3 pm on Thursdays\, 3/12\, 3/26\, 4/9\, 4/23\, 5/14\, and 5/28.\n
 Drop-in sessions\, no registration is required\, but there is limited spac
 e each session.\nFor more information please call 503-644-0043 or ask staf
 f at any service desk.
