DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260326T174500Z
UID:69346e878d33cc4900c532e7@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Get answers to your technology questions! Schedule a 45-minute
  appointment with our friendly Digital Navigator to build your digital ski
 lls. The Digital Navigator can help with installing new apps\, navigating 
 websites\, filling out online job applications\, and more.\nAppointments a
 re on Thursdays at 10am and 11am in the Bethany Library. Register online 
 or by calling 503-617-7323.\nPlease bring your own computer\, tablet\, ce
 llphone\, or e-reader with you to get assistance. Be sure to have any user
 names and passwords available for accounts you need help navigating.\nThe 
 Digital Navigator program is made possible by a partnership between Washin
 gton County Cooperative Library Services and American Connections Corps\,
  an AmeriCorps program dedicated to advancing economic prosperity by bridg
 ing the digital divide.
LOCATION:Bethany Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69346e878d33cc4900c532e7
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
