DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T210000Z
UID:697a9235834cbb3dea2a0765@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:OMSI brings the night sky inside!\nThis unique space science e
 xperience is brought to you with OMSI’s portable\, museum-quality planet
 arium. The portable planetarium brings the night sky inside with live pres
 entations and films.\nThis program is specifically designed for grades K t
 hrough 12 and their families.\nArrive 10 minutes early to get into the por
 table planetarium and settled before it begins. The program will begin pro
 mptly at 1:00 p.m. No late arrivals due to the nature of the program.\nWhe
 n you register\, include yourself and any family members attending.\nEvery
 one welcome.
