UID:692641b196a5073700687e37@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:This season\, the Library Teen Theater Troupe will be putting 
 on a production of The Three Musketeers and the Very Pretty Diamonds by Da
 vid Neilsen. This play is full of humor\, duels\, and trickery. The progra
 m is taught by a professional theater teacher. We will perform for the com
 munity on\nMarch 14\nas part of Hillsboro Reads\, celebrating a shared lov
 e of stories. Please ensure you can make all rehearsal and show dates. All
  experience levels welcome!\nAges 11-18.\nThe troupe will meet starting Ja
 nuary 7th through March 11th.\nStaff Contact:\nKate W
