DESCRIPTION:Bookbabies Fridays at 10:00 a.m.\nMiss Chris guides parents an
 d caregivers through some inspirational early development activities for b
 abies and toddlers. Adults learn techniques that help expand learning expe
 riences at home with their child. Bonus: Visit with other parents and care
 givers while entertaining and educating your little one. Drop in\, no regi
 stration required.\nIf accommodations would help you attend one of our lib
 rary events or classes\, please ask. Our library events are always free!
LOCATION:North Plains Public Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69409f784be11d3d00d84e6b
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
