DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260408T024500Z
UID:69a1e1dc8b29ea2800d2ea13@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:How much do you know about the four themed sets of questions? 
 Themes change monthly. You can play solo but we include hard questions and
  recommend playing as a team (up to 5 people). For Prizes we give out poi
 nts – which can be used at a future trivia night - to those with the hig
 hest and lowest number of correct answers.\nThe freebie question\, answer 
 sheet and meeting details will be emailed to registrants around noon on t
 he day of the event. We will also send this out to late registrants around
  6 pm.
