BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Drop-In Hours with the Social Service Coordinator
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T200000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T220000Z
UID:6998dfa96724c63d00f41be3@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Need assistance with housing\, clothing\, food\, or rent? Look
 ing for health care\, job support\, or simply want someone to talk to? Eve
 ryone is welcome! Join us for our drop-in hours: Wednesdays from 1 PM to 
 3 PM & Fridays from 4 PM to 6 PM Don't miss this chance to connect with r
 esources and community support.\n¿Necesitas ayuda con la vivienda\, la ro
 pa\, la comida o la renta? ¿Buscas atención médica\, apoyo laboral o si
 mplemente quiere hablar con alguien? ¡Todos son bienvenidos! Visítanos 
 nuestro horario los miércoles de 1 p.m. a 3 p.m. y viernes de 4 p.m. a 6 
 p.m. No pierdas la oportunidad de conectarte con recursos y apoyo comunit
 ario.
LOCATION:Cornelius Public Library
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6998dfa96724c63d00f41be3
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
END:VEVENT
