BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:DIY Craftshop: Felted Portraits
DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T180000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T190000Z
UID:6998ff5b5506be0745fe7be3@wccls.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:We are making portraits with wool roving to create a portrait 
 or scene using a wet-felting technique.  Bring a picture of your favorite 
 pet\, mountain\, or person to create a 6" x 8" scene using wool fleece. No
  prior skill needed.\nAll supplies provided. This program is for ages 10 t
 o Adult.\nRegistration required.\nEveryone Welcome.
LOCATION:Sherwood Public Library\, Community Room
URL:https://wccls.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6998ff5b5506be0745fe7be3
X-SOURCE:WCCLS Libraries
